text: Victoria Ostapenco (born 25 October 1994) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Moldova women's national team. ==Career== Ostapenco has been capped for the Moldova national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders
